{"tid":2339825,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣自1997年以來首次擴軍 將於2021年元旦增編2個步兵旅","createTime":"2020-12-25T03:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T07:22:36.000Z","uid":292499,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8ee71cd3472c9d77f0a781199bb8e5eb97bb7115","tid":2339825,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:28:53.000Z","msg":"中共解放軍威脅台灣國防安全日趨嚴重，國防部為此專案報請總統蔡英文核定，2021年元旦在北部地區擴編第109步兵旅及南部地區擴編第117步兵旅。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n這也是自1997年李登輝執政期間開始執行的國軍精實案，迄今24年後，首度在蔡英文任內進行擴編。另外，由於美方今年同意出售岸置魚叉飛彈，作為台灣「岸防巡航飛彈系統」（CDCM，Coastal Defense Cruise Missile），並搭配國軍現在擴編的岸置型雄二、雄三反艦飛彈，因此目前擁有7個岸置雄風飛彈中隊的海鋒大隊，將會大幅擴編，未來主官也將由上校升格為少將。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20201224/FN2KXHWYNZBGBEEBE6GBAODLR4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20201224%2FFN2KXHWYNZBGBEEBE6GBAODLR4%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGtyQscPELFEQk1IFn5y5IyWs%3D&h=4e366cca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20201224%2FFN2KXHWYNZBGBEEBE6GBAODLR4%2F&h=75f8c98b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20201224/FN2KXHWYNZBGBEEBE6GBAODLR4/</a>"},{"pid":"d987a14adaeb41ba4ea4dd3eb33d742471e689a8","tid":2339825,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:29:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527a5b222dc8991245ad75d62f56620dbdf2d2cf","tid":2339825,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/